As long as enchanted land is a basic Mountain, Goblin creatures get +0/+2.
data.flavor_text: The stench of countless generations of unspeakable activities was enough to loosen both our footing and our stomachs.

data.name: Goblin Warchief
data.oracle_text:
Goblin spells you cast cost {1} less to cast.
Goblins you control have haste.
data.flavor_text: Not since the days of Pashalik Mons have the Rundvelt goblins been so united or effective.

data.name: Goblin Chainwhirler
data.oracle_text:
First strike
When this creature enters, it deals 1 damage to each opponent and each creature and planeswalker they control.
data.flavor_text: "The trick is, once you get moving, don't stop!"

data.name: Goblin Barrage
data.oracle_text:
Kicker—Sacrifice an artifact or Goblin. (You may sacrifice an artifact or Goblin in addition to any other costs as you cast this spell.)
Goblin Barrage deals 4 damage to target creature. If this spell was kicked, it also deals 4 damage to target player or planeswalker.

data.name: Bloodstone Goblin
data.oracle_text: Whenever you cast a spell, if that spell was kicked, this creature gets +1/+1 and gains menace until end of turn. (It can't be blocked except by two or more creatures.)
data.flavor_text: The stone whispers tales of darkness and fire. She replies, "Tell me more."

data.name: Sprouting Goblin
data.oracle_text:
Kicker {G} (You may pay an additional {G} as you cast this spell.)
When this creature enters, if it was kicked, search your library for a land card with a basic land type, reveal it, put it into your hand, then shuffle.
{R}, {T}, Sacrifice a land: Draw a card.

data.name: Goblin Picker
data.oracle_text: {R}, {T}, Discard a card: Draw a card.
data.flavor_text: Countless generations of Shivan goblins have worked on the Mana Rig, giving them an unparalleled eye for useful relics.

data.name: Splatter Goblin
data.oracle_text: When this creature dies, target creature an opponent controls gets -1/-1 until end of turn.
data.flavor_text:
"For some, perfection is but a single moment when form and purpose converge."
—Rona

data.name: Goblin Medics
data.oracle_text: Whenever this creature becomes tapped, it deals 1 damage to any target.
data.flavor_text: Dorik was unshakably confident, having learned medicine from the finest butcher shops in Yotia.

data.name: Goblin Turncoat
data.oracle_text: Sacrifice a Goblin: Regenerate this creature.
data.flavor_text: Modo was great at making friends . . . into shields.

data.name: Goblin Test Pilot
data.oracle_text:
Flying
{T}: This creature deals 2 damage to any target chosen at random.
data.flavor_text:
"All pilots and prototypes destroyed. Extensive collateral damage inflicted. Conclusion: flawless design."
—*Manual of Melek*

data.name: Greasewrench Goblin
data.oracle_text: Exhaust — {2}{R}: Discard up to two cards, then draw that many cards. Put a +1/+1 counter on this creature. (Activate each exhaust ability only once.)
data.flavor_text: Killswitch finally had the right wrench for the job. Now she needed to remember what the job was.

data.name: Goblin Surveyor
data.oracle_text:
Trample
Start your engines! (If you have no speed, it starts at 1. It increases once on each of your turns when an opponent loses life. Max speed is 4.)
Max speed — {3}, Exile this card from your graveyard: Draw a card.

data.name: Goblin Welder
data.oracle_text: {T}: Choose target artifact a player controls and target artifact card in that player's graveyard. If both targets are still legal as this ability resolves, that player simultaneously sacrifices the artifact and returns the artifact card to the battlefield.

data.name: Goblin Goon
data.oracle_text:
This creature can't attack unless you control more creatures than defending player.
This creature can't block unless you control more creatures than attacking player.

data.name: Goblin Bombardment
data.oracle_text: Sacrifice a creature: This enchantment deals 1 damage to any target.
data.flavor_text: With one motion, a pest is removed and a scourge inflicted.

data.name: Goblin Electromancer
data.oracle_text: Instant and sorcery spells you cast cost {1} less to cast.
data.flavor_text: When asked how much power is required, Izzet mages always answer "more."

data.name: Goblin Warchief
data.oracle_text:
Goblin spells you cast cost {1} less to cast.
Goblins you control have haste.
data.flavor_text: They poured from the Skirk Ridge like lava, burning and devouring everything in their path.

data.name: Goblin Rimerunner
data.oracle_text:
{T}: Target creature can't block this turn.
{S}: This creature gains haste until end of turn. ({S} can be paid with one mana from a snow source.)
data.flavor_text: Rimerunners set off avalanches to immobilize foes as well as to create more challenging slopes.

data.name: Goblin Furrier
data.oracle_text: Prevent all damage that this creature would deal to snow creatures.
data.flavor_text: Clambering up and over the powdery slope, the goblin chanced upon a small furry thing. There they regarded each other: the goblin and his new pair of earmuffs.

data.name: Goblin Outlander
data.oracle_text: Protection from white
data.flavor_text: Egbol stared in wonder at Naya's landscape. So much to eat. So much to steal.

data.name: Wandering Goblins
data.oracle_text: Domain — {3}: This creature gets +1/+0 until end of turn for each basic land type among lands you control.
data.flavor_text: Tired of waiting for a dragon to eat them, some hardy goblins struck out to become meals for the unknown.

data.name: Goblin Razerunners
data.oracle_text:
{1}{R}, Sacrifice a land: Put a +1/+1 counter on this creature.
At the beginning of your end step, you may have this creature deal damage equal to the number of +1/+1 counters on it to target player or planeswalker.
data.flavor_text: Finding themselves in a new and unexplored world, they immediately set it on fire.

data.name: Goblin Racketeer
data.oracle_text: Whenever this creature attacks, you may goad target creature defending player controls. (Until your next turn, that creature attacks each combat if able and attacks a player other than you if able.)
data.flavor_text: "It, uh, fell off a cart?"

data.name: Toggo, Goblin Weaponsmith
data.oracle_text:
Landfall — Whenever a land you control enters, create a colorless Equipment artifact token named Rock with "Equipped creature has '{1}, {T}, Sacrifice Rock: This creature deals 2 damage to any target'" and equip {1}.
Partner (You can have two commanders if both have partner.)

data.name: Lazier Goblin
data.oracle_text:
Motivate {3}{R} (This creature can't attack or block unless you have paid its motivate cost once. Motivate only as a sorcery.)
When Lazier Goblin enters, it deals 2 damage to any target.

data.name: Goblin Spymaster
data.oracle_text:
First strike
At the beginning of each opponent's end step, that player creates a 1/1 red Goblin creature token with "Creatures you control attack each combat if able."
data.flavor_text:
"Infiltrate and infuriate!"
—Goblin Espionage League motto
